    "At the same time, the reward signal should enable generalisation and avoid reward gaming (i.e.",
    "the exploitation of an unintended loop-hole) as described in [34].",
    "To address these points, we have set up the reward component for MHC as a moving target.",
    "In every step, we compare the MHC at time step t M HC s(t+1) with the best known MHC M HC best of the current episode.",
